 d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614765\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104nec1665702647005.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nec1665702647005.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/nec1665702647005.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"nec1665702647005\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Month Background Color (\n                              MonthBackColor)\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Background color displayed for the month.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nec1665702647005__p_d105743e1_d105744e1_d105745e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>MonthBackColor<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> |\n        <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                     information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rcm1665702587635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" title=\"Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.\">Standard Colors</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"nec1665702647005__table_d12485e1_d12486e1_d12487e1__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a\n                     color.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nec1665702647005__section_et3_5yc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d230165e123\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"nec1665702647005__p_d105749e1_d105750e1_d105751e1\">When not defined, the widget uses the system default\n        colors.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nec1665702647005__section_lbr_vyc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d230165e132\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"nec1665702647005__pre_l2b_xyc_zwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(CALENDAR) = \"MonthBackColor=white\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"nec1665702647005__section_ps2_xyc_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d230165e141\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"svk1665702646925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/svk1665702646925.html\" title=\"The umonthcalendar widget displays a month calendar to enable the user to select a date. Uniface provides a logical widget called MonthCalendar, which is mapped to umonthcalendar.\">(umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Standard Colors</a><p>Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614765\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614765\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Month Background Color ( MonthBackColor) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Month Background Color ( MonthBackColor) Background color displayed for the month. \" MonthBackColor = ColorName | HexColorNumber \" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see Standard Colors . HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. Description When not defined, the widget uses the system default colors. Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(CALENDAR) = \"MonthBackColor=white\" Copy Applies To (umonthcalendar) MonthCalendar Related Links Standard Colors Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}